Flicker/Phoenix/Skyblaze/Pumpskin::

At about that time, Starstorm's backup catches up ...

"HAHAHAHAHA!!!  A battle!  Perfect!  Pumpskin, TERRORIZE!"  The 
crazed Predacon shifts into robot mode, eye lasers blazing at 
Windlord.

Meantime Phoenix sees the one thing that can spur her to battle - a 
friend in danger.  The golden eagle drops from the sky like a 
missile, seeking to bury her talons in Sabre's back.  "Get off her, 
you ... you ..."  The appropriate words to describe her opinion of 
this bot are not in Phoenix's vocabulary.

Flicker and Skyblaze would join the party, but all the good targets 
seem to be taken right now.
